page.title: 12A DAY IN CARE-WELLBURY HOUSE
page.content: {1.35}Back to school,then I chose to go bowling in Stevenage,some others went swimming in our swimming pool. {4.15}We arrived back at Wellbury and played until tea-time. {5.00}We sat down to egg and chips. {6.00}We had another meeting and this time we had to choose an evening activity.I chose to do some cooking. {7.30}We were free to do what we wanted until supper.I cleaned my bedroom,then watched the television. {9.00}We had supper which was chocolate biscuits and coffee made with water not milk. {9.30}Went downstairs to see my baby mice,which are five days old. {10.00}I went to bed. {10.20}The lights were turned off. {10.30}The night lady was comfortably settled and I was asleep. That is a fairly typical day.
